Text: @khairulaming Penting untuk find out land title tu, residential atau commercial title. If commercial title, bil api air akan ikut industrial rate; therefore akan jadi mahal gila. Later boleh convert tapi proses dia makan masa dan leceh.
Translated Text: @khairulaming It's important to find out the land title, residential or commercial title. If it's a commercial title, the fire and water bill will follow the industrial rate; Therefore it will be crazy expensive. Later you can convert but the process takes time and is tedious.

Text: @khairulaming Bila beli rumah strata, in future kalau ada leaking between unit, there is chances yang above unit kena absorb the cost for repairing. Depends on the management punya justification.

Text: bila terjadinya pandemik, semua orang terpaksa lalui fasa perubahan teknologi. cikgu terpaksa mengajar guna webcam, office buat meeting guna webcam, orang jual bundle buat live streaming guna camera, fitness coach buat class pun guna webcam jgk
Translated Text: when a pandemic occurs, everyone has to go through a phase of technological change. teachers have to use webcams to teach, offices use webcams for meetings, people sell bundles for live streaming using cameras, fitness coaches use webcams for classes too

Text: tapi problem bila guna webcam ni, orang assume cara bercakap depan camera ni sama mcm bercakap depan2 in real life. tapi sebenarnya dia jadi sangat2 challenging kalau you dont know how to manage the communication
Translated Text: but the problem is when using this webcam, people assume how to speak in front of the camera is the same as speaking in front of them in real life. but actually it becomes very challenging if you don't know how to manage the communication

Text: sebelum covid wujud, kita rasa gugup nak bercakap depan orang ramai sebab semua orang pandang kita. tapi bila hidup dalam pandemik, kita jadi gugup nak bercakap secara maya sebab tak ada orang nak dengar atau pandang kita. camera off, mic muted, and you berckp sorang2 kat situ
Translated Text: before covid existed, we felt nervous to speak in front of people because everyone looked at us. but when living in a pandemic, we are nervous to speak virtually because no one wants to hear or look at us. camera off, mic muted, and you are alone there

Text: dari situ communication tu dah mula ke laut. online class jadi boring, online meeting jadi boring, online stream jadi boring sbb kita cuma bercakap satu hala and tak engage dengan audience. kat sini aku rasa skill gap besar yang kita kena repair sekarang ni
Translated Text: from there the communication has started to the sea. online class becomes boring, online meeting becomes boring, online stream becomes boring because we only talk one way and do not engage with the audience. here I think there is a big skill gap that we have to repair now

Text: since kita tak tahu bila pandemik ni akan habis, most likely online communication ni akan jadi permanent forever. sbb tu i tekankan kat adik2 untuk develop skill bercakap depan camera ni dari awal. bila masuk uni, nak interview kerja, nak jual barang, everything akan jd online
Translated Text: since we don't know when this pandemic will end, most likely this online communication will be permanent forever. That's why I stress to the sisters to develop the skill of speaking in front of the camera from the beginning. when you enter uni, want to interview for a job, want to sell something, everything will be online

Text: kalau dari awal you biasakan diri untuk maintain eye contact dengan camera, take questions from audience, handle crowd yg tak responsive, beranikan diri tanya soalan, lama2 you akan jadi lagi ‚Äúpresentable‚Äù dalam dunia online. apa2 you nak buat nanti mudah
Translated Text: If from the start you get used to maintaining eye contact with the camera, take questions from the audience, handle unresponsive crowds, have the courage to ask questions, after a while you will become more "presentable" in the online world. what do you want to do later it's easy
